data.description: "Welcome to JB Ranch, an active adult community in southwest Ocala offering new one story, single-family homes!    JB Ranch is an affordable 55+ community featuring a luxury amenity center. Residents stay active with their neighbors and friends at the resort-style pool, fitness center, and pickleball courts." ~ DR Horton    Here is your PERFECT next home! This open floor plan 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home boasts many luxurious upgrades such as granite counters, soaring 9 foot ceilings, plush carpeted bedrooms with tile throughout, espresso colored shaker cabinets, ensuite with his and hers vanities, cordless blinds and much more! The neutral colors throughout bring a relaxing feel to this turn key home. Enjoy any time of the day in your north facing, screened Florida room which offers reprieve from flying pests as well as more consistent shade throughout the day. Have your morning coffee or cozy sunset time overlooking the pristinely landscaped yard including an LED lighted waterfall. This gorgeous home will impress even the most discerning buyer(s). Conveniently located to WEC, Highways, shopping and dining and many additional activates such as day trips to one of the many springs in the area, Crystal River, hiking, kayaking and more. Oh and your groceries? There's a brand new Publix  as well as a Great Clips Salon right across the street for additional convenience. Come walk through and realize "Its home".
